summary: hahaha, i had a dream last night that i was watching (or possibly living in? not sure) the premiere of season 3 of killing eve,...
body:
hahaha, i had a dream last night that i was watching (or possibly living in? not sure) the premiere of season 3 of killing eve, and there was this complicated opening sequence that made it seem like villanelle and eve were trying to hunt each other down or whatever – but THEN it cut to them meeting up and kissing passionately and it was revealed that they were actually a secret team working against some other sinister forces and pretending to still be enemies after some mysterious time jump in the narrative, and i was like, “aaaaaaaaaaaaahhhhh! *ten billion hearteyes emojis*”

honestly, it was pretty rough to wake up into that not being reality.

summary:
I know, I know, shutupaboutkillongeve.jpeg
But may I counter with this:
Consider for a moment the fact that the first time Eve...
body:
I know, I know, shutupaboutkillongeve.jpeg


But may I counter with this:

Consider for a moment the fact that the first time Eve laid eyes on Villanelle in that bathroom she had no idea she was looking at the woman over whom she’d been obsessing. It was just a woman. A woman whose physical appearance Eve took in so completely (for seemingly no reason and in such a short period of time) that she was able to describe her in excruciating detail days later.

Like I know it’s been said that this was love at first sight but baby…….. that’s love at first sight.
